this note interesting.  Since we compete with Big 5 for talent at several 
schools, we should be aware of the make up of some of their job offers that 
lure students to join them.    Paying for a masters degree at UVA ahead of 
time is certainly an interesting piece of this job offer.  See note from Lexi 
below.  
