Dear OU Team:

I just received notice from Jon Beck that he is declining our offer.  He has 
accepted with E&Y in Dallas.  They have offered to pay for his Master's of 
Accounting at the University of Virginia BEFORE he begins working for them.  
This is truly a wonderful opportunity for him, but I know how disappointed 
many of us are to see that he will not be joining the Enron team. 

